Athena
------
* Feature request #50558: DQ2Dataset exclude pattern / extension
  DQ2Dataset.exclude_pattern=['.txt', '.root' ]
  Files patters can now be excluded from DQ2 input dataset
* Fix bug #50449: Pandatools traceback
* Added protections against malformed 'lcg-cr' timeout calls in
  Athena/LCG worker node code, Fixes for PIC
* More robust Athena/LCG worker node code for SL5:
  - jobs are now working at FZK SL5 nodes with DQ2_LOCAL
* TAIWAN-LCG2 now works again with FileStager, but does not with
  DQ2_LOCAL
* Add CPU speed and Architecure to Athena.stats

AthenaMC:
---------
* Added use_partition_numbers to AthenaMCInputDatasets to make Tasks safe
  and still accommodate loose matching.
* AthenaMCDatasets.py: adding proxy lifetime check in outputdata.fill()
  to force the job to abort output dataset registration if the proxy is
  about to be expired.
* wrapper.sh: now catching the exit status code of stage-in.sh to abort job
  execution if any single input data file is missing (Savannah bug 50622).
* stage-out.sh: removing -t timeout flag in lcg-cr as it has been made
  obsolete in the recent version of lcg-utils
* Bug fix: extFile -> extOutFile in AthenaMCPandaRTHandler.py, improving
  logging messages in AthenaMCDatasets.py
* Revisited output site allocation mecanism in LCG (RTHandler), added some
  info level messages to help passing submission time...(MCDatasets and RTHandler)
* Attempt to improve input data downloading by clearing up dead copies from
  failed attempts. Also, reorder list of input sites by forcing local site first.
* Switched off random failing in wrapper.sh on DRYRUN to make GangaTests repeatable

